summary: This mod adds Tel Gothryn - a player owned Telvanni mushroom tower.
descriptionHtml:
[color=green][heading]GENERAL[/heading]
This mod adds a Telvanni mushroom tower to the north of Morthal. It fits well with the swampy area, and is the perfect home for a crazed isolationist Telvanni master wizard.
[/color]
[color=yellow][heading]GOOD TO KNOW[/heading]

* This mod requires the DRAGONBORN DLC to function.
* The Chests named \"Personal Belongings are safe to store items in.

[/color]

[heading]WHAT WE HAVE SO FAR[/heading]
[color=green]
[list] [*] Dining area,
[*] Alchemy and Enchanting laboratory,
[*] Library/Study,
[*] Kitchen + Follower\'s bedroom,
[*] Bedroom,
[*] Misc: Waterwalking spell (on a table near a bookcase), Telvanni robes, \"Personal Belongings\" storage chests [/list]
[/color]
[heading]Update Log[/heading]

-Version 1.0
-Version 1.1 (Fixed the float bug, Working Waterwalking spell.
